text: Dane Willard Boedigheimer (born September 28, 1978), better known by their cybernym DaneBoe, is an American filmmaker, singer and actor. They are known for creating the web series The Annoying Orange and the spin-off television series The High Fructose Adventures of Annoying Orange.
